posts.subject: 4chan is compromized
posts.body:
All threads mentioning targeted chat bots on 4chan get repeatedly deleted (like rather harmless thread in pic related). I think we are onto something here.

Specifically the Nazi spam on 4chan is apparently targeted in a way to portray Trump supporters or other groups simply acting in self interest as "Hitler followers".
E.g. the endless "<insert minority here> hate" threads are totally artificial. They are planted to make people look like degenerate idiots.
How can I "reroute" my zeronet traffic through privoxy so that other devices can access it?

What everybody needs to know is that your IP gets also published when connecting via tor.
That is one of the reasons why torrenting over tor makes no sense.
Publishing your IP is actually part of the bittorrent protocol.
Explanation here: https://blog.torproject.org/bittorrent-over-tor-isnt-good-idea
